From cb1bd538a96fddd02ef2178ab138d19e53bd0611 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Mingcong Bai <jeffbai@aosc.io>
Date: Sat, 10 May 2025 17:15:04 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 345/376] AOSCOS: LOONGARCH64_NOSIMD: pwm: pwm-loongson: remove
 pwm_loongson_suspend_store in pwm_loongson_ddata

From v9 of the LoongArch PWM patchset, "pwm: Add Loongson PWM controller
support" removed `struct pwm_loongson_suspend_store'. However, this struct
is still used by "feat(pwm): pwm capture(WIP)".

Remove this struct from pwm_loongson_ddata to fix build.

Fixes: "feat(pwm): pwm capture(WIP)"
Signed-off-by: Mingcong Bai <jeffbai@aosc.io>
Signed-off-by: Ilikara <3435193369@qq.com>
---
 drivers/pwm/pwm-loongson.c | 1 -
 1 file changed, 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/drivers/pwm/pwm-loongson.c b/drivers/pwm/pwm-loongson.c
index e00e95354eb8..858a54ebeab0 100644
--- a/drivers/pwm/pwm-loongson.c
+++ b/drivers/pwm/pwm-loongson.c
@@ -58,7 +58,6 @@ struct pwm_loongson_ddata {
 	u32 irq;
 	u32 int_count;
 	u64 clk_rate;
-	struct pwm_loongson_suspend_store lss;
 	struct wait_queue_head capture_wait_queue;
 };
 
-- 
